    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3 powered by the S54 3.2L atmospheric inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS for an 8,000 RPM redline. This example maintains excellent torsional rigidity, with a reinforced rear subframe and a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein dampers and poly-bushings for sharpened turn-in. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a M-Variable limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and a cooling system overhaul to ensure thermal efficiency during spirited driving. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the powertrain and drivetrain remain in peak operational form.",
